cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.CV 

The paper deals with security issues in wireless sensor networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed solution involves embedding data in an image, which involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The transmission of data is done over the network, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The evaluation of the proposed method involves image quality metrics, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV).
